tourBios.curYrHigh: Competing as an amateur, he earned PGA TOUR Latinoamérica status with a T18 finish at the Argentina Q-School in January... His first start on PGA TOUR Latinoamérica was also his first as a professional at the Lexus Panama Classic in March.
tourBios.personal: Has one brother, Travis... His wife, Brittney, is his trainer and nutritionist. She is also a triathlete... Loves to cook at home... His favorite golf memory is playing a Pro-Am with Jack Nicklaus at Carlton Woods... Would like to trade places for a day with Jordan Spieth to see his ability first hand... The Floridian and Dallas National are his favorite golf courses... Payton Manning is his favorite athlete outside of golf... The Houston Texans and the Houston Rockets are his favorite professional teams... Supports the Woodforest Charitable Foundation, which was started by his in-laws.
